        "purpose": "modern_jp_reading",
        "value": "内譯（ないやく）— 六大隊の内訳"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "english_translation",
        "value": "Breakdown (内譯) — the header introducing the six itemized corps that follow: 士官 864 + 砲士 180 + 兵士 1,440 + 砲卒 108 + 兵卒 260 + 樂卒 120 = 2,972 personnel. With 36 cannon, this is the army that overturned the long-held belief that Hansei Ichiran recorded no force for Saga. (2,972 is the sum of the listed corps; the page prints the items, not a separate total.)"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "extracted_value",
