        "purpose": "english_translation",
        "value": "Sakura domain (Hotta family, Shimōsa) — a DIFFERENT domain. Its ○ marker begins HERE; everything to its RIGHT on this page is the tail of the PREVIOUS entry — Saga. This right-to-left page-spill is exactly why Saga's army went unnoticed for years (searches used the old-kanji 佐嘉; the Table-9 fascicle prints 佐賀)."
